Package: blbglmpar
Type: Package
Title: Fitting Generalized Linear Models Using Bootstrap
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Abdul-Hakeem Omotayo
Maintainer: The package maintainer <sqoma@rocketmail.com>
Description: blbglmpar is used to fit generalized linear models, 
    specified by giving a symbolic description of the linear predictor and a description of the error distribution. blbglmpar also has parallelization capabilities.
